name: Origin Analyses Theme File
summary: Learn about .OIS files and view a list of programs that open them.

content: You most likely will never encounter an OIS theme file when using Origin. The file is not meant to be opened by the user. Instead, it stores the settings that are referenced by Origin for analyses.
NOTE: OIS files are typically located in the "AnalysisAndReportTable" folder of the C:\​Program Files\​OriginLab\​Origin <version>\​Themes installation.
